**Summary of the change - Iteration 566: "Add sentence-by-sentence playback panel to Listening Quiz"**

**What it does:**
- Adds a collapsible "Sentence Breakdown" panel to the Listening Quiz page (both listen and quiz phases)
- Users can expand to see individual sentences extracted from the passage
- Each sentence has a play button for individual TTS playback at the current speed
- Visual highlighting shows which sentence is currently playing

